हेलो! मैंने Kuku FM (Android)  पर यह शो सुना और मुझे यकीन है कि आपको भी यह जरूर पसंद आएगा।

show.description: Once living a humble life as a street sweeper, Rudra Randhawa hides a powerful secret. He is the legendary Supreme Leader, a man who once shaped nations. When his new wife Maanvi Chauhan and her daughter Anika are drawn into a web of betrayal, greed, and family feuds, Rudra steps out of the shadows to protect them, revealing his true power and rewriting their destinies. Watch Now!
